e the glitch effect from text?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "If you copy and paste glitch text into a raw text editor, you can manually delete the characters from right to left, slowly stripping away the combining marks until the original base character is revealed. Some online tools are also designed specifically to strip away Unicode modifiers and restore the base text automatically."}}]}, {"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Article", "headline": "Glitch Text Generator: Transform Your Text Into Zalgo Art"}];
